title: Fly Me To The Moon
lyrics:
[intro] (Em)
 
(Em)Fly me to the (Am7)moon, and let me (D7)play among the (Gmaj7)stars
(Cmaj7) Let me see what (Am7)spring is like on (B7) Jupiter and (Em)Mars
In (Am7)other words, (D7) hold my (Gmaj7)hand
In (Am7)other words, (D7) baby (Gmaj7)kiss me (B7)
 
(Em)Fill my heart with (Am7)song, and let me (D7)sing forever (Gmaj7)more
(Cmaj7)You're all that I (Am7)long for, all I (B7)worship and a(Em)dore
In (Am7)other words, (D7) please be (Bm)true! (E7)
In (Am7)other words, (D) I love (G)you! (B7)
 
(Em)Fill my heart with (Am7)song, and let me (D7)sing forever (Gmaj7)more
(Cmaj7)You're all that I (Am7)long for, all I (B7)worship and a(Em)dore
In (Am7)other words, (D7) please be (Bm)true! (E7)
In (Am7)other words (D) I love (G)you! (E7)
[slow down]
In (Am7)other words (D-stop) I love (G - tremolo)you! [end]
